15#ifndef ISC_RESULT_H
16#define ISC_RESULT_H 1
17
18/*! \file isc/result.h */
19
20#include <isc/lang.h>
21#include <isc/types.h>
22
23#define ISC_R_SUCCESS 0 /*%< success */
24#define ISC_R_NOMEMORY 1 /*%< out of memory */
25#define ISC_R_TIMEDOUT 2 /*%< timed out */
26#define ISC_R_NOTHREADS 3 /*%< no available threads */
27#define ISC_R_ADDRNOTAVAIL 4 /*%< address not available */
28#define ISC_R_ADDRINUSE 5 /*%< address in use */
29#define ISC_R_NOPERM 6 /*%< permission denied */
30#define ISC_R_NOCONN 7 /*%< no pending connections */
31#define ISC_R_NETUNREACH 8 /*%< network unreachable */
32#define ISC_R_HOSTUNREACH 9 /*%< host unreachable */
33#define ISC_R_NETDOWN 10 /*%< network down */
34#define ISC_R_HOSTDOWN 11 /*%< host down */
35#define ISC_R_CONNREFUSED 12 /*%< connection refused */
36#define ISC_R_NORESOURCES 13 /*%< not enough free resources */
37#define ISC_R_EOF 14 /*%< end of file */
38#define ISC_R_BOUND 15 /*%< socket already bound */
39#define ISC_R_RELOAD 16 /*%< reload */
40#define ISC_R_SUSPEND ISC_R_RELOAD /*%< alias of 'reload' */
41#define ISC_R_LOCKBUSY 17 /*%< lock busy */
42#define ISC_R_EXISTS 18 /*%< already exists */
43#define ISC_R_NOSPACE 19 /*%< ran out of space */
44#define ISC_R_CANCELED 20 /*%< operation canceled */
45#define ISC_R_NOTBOUND 21 /*%< socket is not bound */
46#define ISC_R_SHUTTINGDOWN 22 /*%< shutting down */
47#define ISC_R_NOTFOUND 23 /*%< not found */
48#define ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND 24 /*%< unexpected end of input */
49#define ISC_R_FAILURE 25 /*%< generic failure */
50#define ISC_R_IOERROR 26 /*%< I/O error */
51#define ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED 27 /*%< not implemented */
52#define ISC_R_UNBALANCED 28 /*%< unbalanced parentheses */
53#define ISC_R_NOMORE 29 /*%< no more */
54#define ISC_R_INVALIDFILE 30 /*%< invalid file */
55#define ISC_R_BADBASE64 31 /*%< bad base64 encoding */
56#define ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDTOKEN 32 /*%< unexpected token */
57#define ISC_R_QUOTA 33 /*%< quota reached */
58#define ISC_R_UNEXPECTED 34 /*%< unexpected error */
59#define ISC_R_ALREADYRUNNING 35 /*%< already running */
60#define ISC_R_IGNORE 36 /*%< ignore */
61#define ISC_R_MASKNONCONTIG 37 /*%< addr mask not contiguous */
62#define ISC_R_FILENOTFOUND 38 /*%< file not found */
63#define ISC_R_FILEEXISTS 39 /*%< file already exists */
64#define ISC_R_NOTCONNECTED 40 /*%< socket is not connected */
65#define ISC_R_RANGE 41 /*%< out of range */
66#define ISC_R_NOENTROPY 42 /*%< out of entropy */
67#define ISC_R_MULTICAST 43 /*%< invalid use of multicast */
68#define ISC_R_NOTFILE 44 /*%< not a file */
69#define ISC_R_NOTDIRECTORY 45 /*%< not a directory */
70#define ISC_R_QUEUEFULL 46 /*%< queue is full */
71#define ISC_R_FAMILYMISMATCH 47 /*%< address family mismatch */
72#define ISC_R_FAMILYNOSUPPORT 48 /*%< AF not supported */
73#define ISC_R_BADHEX 49 /*%< bad hex encoding */
74#define ISC_R_TOOMANYOPENFILES 50 /*%< too many open files */
75#define ISC_R_NOTBLOCKING 51 /*%< not blocking */
76#define ISC_R_UNBALANCEDQUOTES 52 /*%< unbalanced quotes */
77#define ISC_R_INPROGRESS 53 /*%< operation in progress */
78#define ISC_R_CONNECTIONRESET 54 /*%< connection reset */
79#define ISC_R_SOFTQUOTA 55 /*%< soft quota reached */
80#define ISC_R_BADNUMBER 56 /*%< not a valid number */
81#define ISC_R_DISABLED 57 /*%< disabled */
82#define ISC_R_MAXSIZE 58 /*%< max size */
83#define ISC_R_BADADDRESSFORM 59 /*%< invalid address format */
84#define ISC_R_BADBASE32 60 /*%< bad base32 encoding */
85#define ISC_R_UNSET 61 /*%< unset */
86#define ISC_R_MULTIPLE 62 /*%< multiple */
87#define ISC_R_WOULDBLOCK 63 /*%< would block */
88#define ISC_R_COMPLETE 64 /*%< complete */
89#define ISC_R_CRYPTOFAILURE 65 /*%< cryptography library failure */
90#define ISC_R_DISCQUOTA 66 /*%< disc quota */
91#define ISC_R_DISCFULL 67 /*%< disc full */
92
93/*% Not a result code: the number of results. */
94#define ISC_R_NRESULTS 68
